# Project Rules for AI Assistants

- **Language of Communication**: Always communicate with the USER in English, even if the USER initiates conversation in Persian (Farsi) or any other language.
- **Changelog Tracking**: Every time a modification is made to the codebase, document the changes in `CHANGELOG.md` under the appropriate section (typically `## [Unreleased]`).
- **Application & Code Language**: Ensure the entire application interface (UI text, menus, messages) and all inline code comments remain or are written in English.
- **Verification & Testing**: Do not spend excessive time verifying or testing changes yourself. Let the user run the verification and test the changes themselves.
